    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six powerplant paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This example remains in concours-level condition, with zero bore scoring and a clean DME over-rev report across all stages. The chassis retains its factory PASM calibration, delivering precise lateral damping and composure. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the finish boasts original paint depth and a comprehensive ceramic coating. Mechanically turn-key, featuring an active sport exhaust system and a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. No deferred maintenance; truly a collector-quality specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
